- Don't u feel a little bored and frustratied travelling alone? Like u need to share your emotions, but there is nobody. I've tried travelling with friends and by myself. And in a group it's much more fun. But it's so hard to find that company.
- Oh, I feel exactly the same. Though I really like being alone, it's difficult and saddening to experience all the beauty by yourself. 'Happiness only real when shared'. I really wish to travel with someone, but it's extremely difficult to find a right person, and if you find wrong one, your trip may be ruined. I made this mistake once and I really would prefer to travel alone that time. But once you're with a person who suits you, travelling becomes even more deep and beautiful.
